high_descs: Walk straight to the bed, then turn left at the foot of the bed and go to the night stand by the head of the bed.
Pick up the pen on the night stand, close to the edge, and beside the keys.
Turn to your left and walk to the desk.
Place the pen on the desk, above the credit card.
Turn around and walk back to the night stand.
Pick up the pen on the night stand, beside the lamp.
Turn to your left and go back to the desk.
Place the pen on the desk, in front of the other pen.
anns.task_desc: Move two pens from the night stand to the desk.
